snippet.title: Bubbleshot (Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
Bubbleshot 1.0.0 is releasing on GameJolt on October 25, 2024. https://gamejolt.com/games/bubbleshot/933666

You live in someone’s immune system. Everyone is happy and go-lucky, until suddenly, a deadly disease attacks the town, and you’re the only one to save everyone. #games #gaming #gamejolt #bubbleshot #animation #shorts
